<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Health Web MVP</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* 確保在電腦上看也是手機大小 */
        body { background-color: #f3f4f6; }
        .mobile-container { max-width: 414px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 100vh; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="mobile-container relative pb-20">
    <header class="bg-green-700 text-white p-4 sticky top-0 z-10 shadow-md">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="text-sm opacity-80"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left mr-2"></i> 返回 HG App</div>
            <div class="font-bold text-lg">Happy Health 專區</div>
            <div><i class="fas fa-bell"></i></div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-3 text-xs text-gray-600 border-b border-yellow-200">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle text-yellow-500 mr-1"></i> 
        <strong>系統串接說明：</strong> HG App 透過 URL 帶入參數 
        <code class="bg-yellow-100 px-1 rounded text-red-600">?hg_id=user123&token=abc</code>
    </div>

    <div class="p-4">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-500 rounded-xl p-4 text-white shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-xl font-bold mr-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">早安，HG 會員</h2>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-80">HG ID: user123</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/20 rounded-lg p-2 flex justify-between items-center">
                <span class="text-sm">健康積分 (Happy Score)</span>
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-300"><i class="fas fa-coins mr-1"></i> 350</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="px-4 py-2">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 text-lg">今日健康任務</h3>
        
        <a href="https://chrysyehddim-pm.github.io/ad8test/" target="_blank" class="block bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-3 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
            <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mr-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-store"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">幸福柑仔店</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">極早期失智篩檢 (AD8)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                    <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-bold">+50 Pts</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://chrysyehddim-pm.github.io/memory/" target="_blank" class="block bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-3 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
            <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 text-teal-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mr-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">生活記憶力訓練</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">大腦活化鍛鍊</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                    <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-bold">+20 Pts</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://chrysyehddim-pm.github.io/Squat-Game-PoC/" target="_blank" class="block bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-3 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
            <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mr-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-child"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">金幣深蹲王</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">AI 鏡頭核心肌群訓練</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                    <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-bold">+30 Pts</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
